Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:43.61,IN_EN_EP11,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\fax-0.15}Greensleeves was my delight,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.61,0:01:49.69,IN_EN_EP11,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3\fax-0.15}Greensleeves was my heart of gold,
